query:
SELECT
            m.model_name,
            u.total_input_tokens,
            u.total_output_tokens,
            u.created_at
        FROM
            usage u
        JOIN
            models m ON u.model_id = m.model_id
        JOIN
            users usr ON u.user_id = usr.user_id
        WHERE
            usr.email = $1
            AND date_trunc('month', u.created_at) = date_trunc('month', now())
        ORDER BY
            u.created_at DESC
        LIMIT $2
